The paper deals with the problem of detecting and estimating the position of robots in a 2D camera image, which is a common problem in robotics and automation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for object detection and transfer learning for re-training the network for different robot types, which falls under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the possible applications of the proposed method in various fields, which could be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
